75
00:16:53,256 --> 00:16:56,748
I don't have anything
more to tell you two.

76
00:16:56,793 --> 00:17:00,229
What a terrible morning this has been.

77
00:17:01,164 --> 00:17:02,688
Take a look at this woman.

78
