88
00:17:51,714 --> 00:17:54,410
Come on, a criminal wouldn't
dress so conspicuously.

89
00:17:55,051 --> 00:18:00,956
Whatever. But I study art,
and I never mistake a color!

90
00:18:01,758 --> 00:18:05,353
You've asked enough questions,
now how about leaving me alone?

91
00:18:37,460 --> 00:18:39,655
Why red clothes?

92
00:18:39,696 --> 00:18:44,861
She's not a firewoman.
Red... red... red...

93
00:19:01,384 --> 00:19:03,682
A red shirt.

94
00:19:09,759 --> 00:19:12,227
On Sale Now!

95
00:19:32,582 --> 00:19:36,177
That's enough for today. I'm going home.

96
00:19:43,793 --> 00:19:47,126
That's strange. I'm sure it was closed.

97
00:20:25,468 --> 00:20:28,801
This red bathing suit
sure is something else!

98
00:20:28,838 --> 00:20:32,672
Bet she's going to take it off soon!

99
00:20:34,110 --> 00:20:36,806
Narita! What are you looking at?

100
00:20:40,516 --> 00:20:42,984
Iijima! What are you wearing that for?!

101
00:20:43,519 --> 00:20:46,920
What do you mean?
What's wrong with my outfit?

102
00:20:52,962 --> 00:20:54,190
Oh, it's a white tank top.

103
00:20:56,399 --> 00:21:00,358
Too bad. Just an afterimage.

104
00:21:33,302 --> 00:21:36,931
Iijima! It was an afterimage!

105
00:21:37,440 --> 00:21:41,900
Hoshino was the killer after all!
Let's get back to college!

106
00:21:45,214 --> 00:21:46,112
