107
00:23:02,959 --> 00:23:04,256
What was that?

108
00:23:04,293 --> 00:23:05,453
Oh no!

109
00:23:41,264 --> 00:23:42,822
How did you figure it out?

110
00:23:43,366 --> 00:23:45,493
I was too late, Iijima.

111
00:23:45,534 --> 00:23:48,264
If only I'd figured it out
a little sooner.

112
00:23:54,210 --> 00:23:55,177
Narita.

113
00:24:09,859 --> 00:24:13,590
How'd you know that
Hoshino was the killer?

114
00:24:13,896 --> 00:24:16,694
It was an afterimage.

115
00:24:16,732 --> 00:24:18,529
