116
00:24:19,335 --> 00:24:22,395
Like when you stare at
something yellow...

117
00:24:22,438 --> 00:24:24,407
...then look away at something white.

118
00:24:24,407 --> 00:24:26,705
For an instant, it appears blue.

119
00:24:26,742 --> 00:24:28,437
