must be Mika Hoshino!

127
00:25:03,112 --> 00:25:04,773
Maybe.

128
00:25:04,814 --> 00:25:08,648
We've got to do something
before she kills someone else.

129
00:25:08,684 --> 00:25:09,514
But...

130
00:25:09,785 --> 00:25:10,547
But?

131
00:25:11,187 --> 00:25:15,351
