152
00:28:43,632 --> 00:28:44,792
Narita!

153
00:28:48,671 --> 00:28:50,195
My panties.

154
00:28:52,541 --> 00:28:54,008
You're depraved!

155
00:29:08,691 --> 00:29:12,127
Fine Arts Club

156
00:29:17,633 --> 00:29:19,225
Mika Hoshino.

157
00:29:24,640 --> 00:29:26,699
I've been waiting for you.

158
00:29:28,777 --> 00:29:30,108
You have?

159
00:29:30,913 --> 00:29:34,110
I need to talk to you.

160
00:29:39,355 --> 00:29:42,654
I've had my eye on you.

161
00:29:44,727 --> 00:29:45,659
Hoshino.

162
00:29:46,662 --> 00:29:51,099
I get so flustered and confused
when I think of you.

163
00:29:51,667 --> 00:29:55,125
That's strange. Not a tentacle in sight.

164
00:29:57,172 --> 00:29:59,003
My heart aches for you.

165
00:29:59,642 --> 00:30:03,476
Okay, I get it. But I don't
think this is the time to...

166
