170
00:30:28,404 --> 00:30:29,166
Hoshino!

171
00:30:30,072 --> 00:30:34,566
I won't let anyone else have you!

172
00:30:37,046 --> 00:30:41,745
Damn, I can't move! It was you, Hoshino!

173
00:30:57,466 --> 00:30:58,490
Narita!

174
00:31:29,298 --> 00:31:30,595
Narita!

175
00:31:34,870 --> 00:31:36,360
Narita! Narita!

176
00:31:38,640 --> 00:31:40,005
It might not be too late!

177
00:31:40,909 --> 00:31:44,970
I'll give him this ball,
left from the last replinoid.

178
00:31:47,616 --> 00:31:49,413
